sdp/verification/t-010@20260515t214233z-verify.md:17:1. `promptclaw pal diagnose slow-inference PROJECT_ROOT` writes a complete run artifact set including `input/task.md`, `routing/route.json`, `routing/route.md`, `outputs/slow-inference-diagnosis.json`, `handoffs/slow-inference-diagnosis.md`, `summary/final-summary.md`, `logs/events.jsonl`, `state.json`. Both the payload and route record `mutating_actions: []`. Test `test_pal_slow_inference_diagnosis_writes_artifact_and_declares_no_mutation` confirms every file and field. ✓
sdp/verification/t-010@20260515t214233z-verify.md:21:3. CLI summary and `--json` modes both work correctly. `cmd_pal_diagnose_slow_inference` prints `run_id`, `status`, `severity`, `finding_count`, `executed_tools`, `mutating_actions`, `diagnosis` path, `summary` path, and returns appropriate exit codes. ✓
